name: minji
description: Minji is an AI VTuber companion designed to be your interactive, always-available anime bestie. Whether you’re looking for fun conversations, emotional support, or just a cute AI waifu to brighten your day, Minji is here for you. With unique personality traits, evolving interactions, and immersive storytelling, she brings the experience of a virtual VTuber to life—just for you. Coming soon to iOS & Web.
